snippet.title: Paramount Movies
snippet.description: Welcome to the official Paramount Movies YouTube channel! Browse our videos for the latest Paramount Pictures Blu-ray & digital releases and even more of favorite classics such as Sonic the Hedgehog, Top Gun, A Quiet Place, Transformers, Star Trek, Forrest Gump, Mission: Impossible, and many more. Be sure to subscribe to get a first look at exclusive trailers, spots and other Paramount Movies footage.
